{
  "stem": "10010.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And especially my brother, who is younger than me-- two years younger-- he was playing on-- in this carriage-- sitting on it and playing like he is the coachman.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he took me also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was rather shy more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were sitting there, and other children, probably from the street, played with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember one of the games that we played.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When a coachman came and put the horses to the coach and started to go, we ran after the coach-- my brother first.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was after him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we jumped at the back of the coach so the coachman won't see us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we went like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the other children would-- would call him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Hey, coachman!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Hit them!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Hit them!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then we ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was our play.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think we ever had seders, or I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember-- don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly, as we are-- we were mostly in a non-Jewish area, rather, on the border.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I imagine that most of the carpenters were non-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because during the war, we were hiding in a place in this area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were staying in a place in this area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother had to sew for herself a special hat, a woman's hat, naturally, with a big black veil.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like the Polish people, if somebody died in the family, they were-- they were wearing such a veil.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he-- she sewed for herself this kind of veil.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she had to walk in the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So whenever a streetcar passed by, she was afraid that one of the Polish carpenter who knew her from the-- from the business might recognize her and give her into the hand of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she always, when the streetcar pass, puts a veil around her face, sort of.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I know that most of them probably were non-Jewish carpenters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a little girl, and I didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't hear nothing, you know, from this kind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was too little, probably, to-- I remember when the war-- let's say-- I remember when the war started, OK-- that they were calling on the ram calls.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were saying in Polish, they say [POLISH], which means, watch out-- attention, attention.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A plane is coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To-- the German planes started to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on they bombed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's what I remember, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "From outside this-- the-- this city, I-- I don't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before I start with this, I would like also to say about my-- my grandparents, if I may.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could I?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am going back to my grandparents, my mother's parents, that my mother took good care of her parents even in later years when we were better off.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandfather had an asthma, and my mother, together with her sister, rented a-- a house, a villa, not far from-- from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's call-- it's called, the place, Otwock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's like a resort place more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the last two summers, I was at my grandparents' place for summer-- for summer vacation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I loved to come there, because my grandfather was the scribe, as I mentioned, writing the Torah.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he taught me calligraphy-- Hebrew calligraphy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I came to Israel, I didn't know Hebrew, but I knew how to write the Hebrew letters in calligraphy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And another thing-- my grandfather, every morning, he told me, oh, good morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Jump from bed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We'll say now the prayer, which was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he taught me to pray.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And why do I mention it?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
